1. *Svega* se osećam iscrpljeno. (I feel exhausted about everything.) 
2. *Svega* se desilo za samo nekoliko minuta. (Everything happened within just a few minutes.)
3. Nije bilo *svega* što me je zanimalo. (There wasn't everything that I was interested in.)
4. Ona je znala *svega* o tome. (She knew everything about it.)
5. *Svega* mi je bilo dovoljno. (It was enough for me.)